arStrings.szText:
While moving you generate Fury, increased based on distance and speed.

Moving while {c_important}{u}Unstoppable{/u}{/c} creates {c_important}Earthquakes{/c} beneath you that deal {c_number}500%{/c} of your Thorns as Physical damage over {c_number}[PowerTag.Barbarian_Earthquake."Script Formula 1"]{/c} seconds.
